creator: Agcocorp Inc
descriptionHtml: Fendt Connect app allows you to track your machine data remotely where ever you are in the world. Fendt Connect app is official Fendt Connect telemetry system app. With this app you can connect to your tractor and receive fuel consumption, driving data, GSP location, service codes and much more. To fully utilize the Fendt Connect app you need to login at www. fendtconnect.com to create your account.

Support for registration and account management
Bug fixes
